---
title: Index
---
.content
  .block.block-hero
    h1 We deliver clear, effective design solutions. We create user focussed websites and apps, develop beautiful branding and produce precise print design.

  h3.headline Fresh Projects

  .case-studies
    - data.projects.each do |project|
      .block.block-inset
        a href= project["title"].parameterize
          .b-thumb
            == image_tag project["thumb"], alt: project["title"]
        .b-text
          h3.headline= project["title"]
          p= project["intro"]
          a href= project["title"].parameterize class="project_link icon-arrow-right" VIEW THE PROJECT

  .clients
    h3.headline Our clients include:
    - data.clients.each do |client|
      .grid-item
        .block.block-inset
          .b-thumb
            == image_tag client["logo"], alt: client["name"]
